            <title>[STORM-3775] topology.blobstore.map can cause supervisor restarts</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STORM-3775</link>
                <project id="12314820" key="STORM">Apache Storm</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I noticed that setting a blobstore map config with booleans formatted as strings would be accepted and cause the AsyncLocalizer to throw an exception and cause supervisor restarts.&#160; The config option should not be valid and prevent being submitted.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
topology.blobstore.map&lt;br/&gt;
        {  &quot;blob1&quot;: &lt;/p&gt;
{    &quot;localname&quot;: &quot;test.tgz&quot;,     &quot;uncompress&quot;: &quot;false&quot;  }
&lt;p&gt;}&lt;/p&gt;</description>
